MARCFieldLabel: DATE/TIME AND PLACE OF AN EVENT NOTE (R)
Transformation Notes:
Prepend a, d, o, p, 1 with subfield label:  
If $0, prepend with "Authority record control number or standard number for controlled place of event term:"
If $2, prepend with "Source of term for controlled place of event term:"
If $3, append (Applies to: [$3 value]) to note.

MARCFieldLabel: DATE/TIME AND PLACE OF AN EVENT NOTE (R)
MARCSubfieldLabel: Authority record control number or standard number (R)
Transformation Notes:
If $0 then add this to the description of the nomen: 
[Nomen] --> has related nomen of nomen --> "$0 value"
Notes (Uncategorized): Control number of the record for a controlled place term in subfield $p.

MARCFieldLabel: DATE/TIME AND PLACE OF AN EVENT NOTE (R)
MARCSubfieldLabel: Place of event (R), Source of term (R)
Transformation Notes:
If 0 can be identified as a place (based on rdf:type)
[Expression] → has related place of expression → [Place] 
[Place] → has access point rdap:P70018 → [Nomen]
[Nomen] → has nomen string → [$p value]

MARCFieldLabel: DATE/TIME AND PLACE OF AN EVENT NOTE (R)
MARCSubfieldLabel: Place of event (R), Source of term (R)
Transformation Notes:
[Expression] → has related place of expression → [Place] 
[Place] → has access point rdap:P70018 → [Nomen]
[Nomen] → has nomen string → [$p value]
[Nomen] → has scheme of nomen → [URI for source of the term in $p]
